Title: Kubernetes: agent: handle pending pods
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1621602628
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p5

Before this werk, the kubernetes special agent could not handle pods that are
pending. The error message was:

<tt>TypeError: '&lt;' not supported between instances of 'NoneType' and 'str'</tt>

This should now be fixed.
